\|x\|_p^p = |x_1|^p + |x_2|^p
\left( \frac{\|Ax\|_p}{\|x\|_p} \right)^p = \frac{(|2x_1 + x_2|)^p + (|x_1 + 2x_2|)^p}{|x_1|^p + |x_2|^p}
x_1 = x_2 = y
